5. What is the purpose of the layers drop-down in the editor toolbar?

- Allows you to filter the visible objects

6. What is the purpose of this button?

- Step through frames

7. Which shortcut plays a game?

- CTRL + P

8. Which shortcut pauses a game?

- CTRL + SHIFT + P
